text: Anna Jurkiewicz (born February 9, 1984 in Oświęcim, Poland) is a Polish figure skater. As a young girl, she was one of the best young skaters in the world. Then she had some health problems and was not able to skate. She returned in 2006 and has been competing internationally since autumn 2006. == Other websites == * Official Homepage * ISU Official Profile Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Polish sportspeople Category:Figure skaters
